title: [House Brigatta, Lane]
description: Stepping into the lane, you stand in front of a cozy looking, trim house of modest proportions.  A small brass sign, neatly engraved, announces: House Brigatta.

At the end of the lane stands a cozy-looking, trim house of modest proportions with a neatly painted door bearing a polished brass bell.  A small brass sign, neatly engraved, announces, "House Brigatta."  A garden path leads through a rose-vined, wrought iron gate.
